{
  "stem": "18581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 421.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we simply left the place, which afterwards was abandoned anyway and the people were sent back to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the peat mine was-- it belonged to-- it was occupied, so according to the laws of occupation, it belonged to the occupying Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was regarded Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it was run by OT, that means Organisation Todt, the Todt organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were doing some earth-moving and other mine work for the Germans in the east.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- then I worked most of the time cutting the peat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then they-- they discovered they needed someone who spoke Lithuanian and German and Polish, which I did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I believe that I managed to be maybe a week in the office, where I heard a little more as to what was going on, what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was one of the reasons why we ran away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to a place called Kalelishok.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-A-L-E-S-H-I-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --shok, S-H-O-K.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kalelishok.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There we stayed for a few weeks with some Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, the Jews were told that they have to move to Dzieveniskes, D-Z-I-E-V-E-N-I-S-K-E-S, Dzieveniskes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to Dzieveniskes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Dzieveniskes, apparently the Germans received instructions to concentrate the-- the Jews from the surrounding areas in bigger towns, major sort of central provincetowns.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were brought to Varenavas, or in Yiddish [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "V-A-R-E-N-A-V-A-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably-- I'm trying to think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Probably in January or February.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'42.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my father stayed in town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the-- the Judenrat asked for 30 to 40 people, young people, to go out to work in the vicinity, 10 kilometers, in the-- with the forester.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I had a discussion with my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- of course I wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
